SafeHouse Explorer hides and protects your private documents and files, keeping them safe from intruders and anyone else who doesn't have your permission to view them. Trust your privacy to SafeHouse.

SafeHouse Explorer creates hidden private storage areas on your hard drive to hold your confidential files. Your files are completely invisible until you enter your password.

INSTALLING SAFEHOUSE EXPLORER




Please know that this setup program will not touch any of your existing files.
